As ofte as a man þoth hem mynne.Any man dothe them be-gynne. L. adds:
And with gode Devocion seith þem to the ende,
Then may the soules to hevyn wende;
Therfore this Salme haue ye in thought;
The xv Salmes for-yete ye nought;
The letany also ye haue in mynde,
Loke thou leve hit not be-hynde.

